      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe, finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather. This example is powered by the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. The chassis is structurally pristine with a reinforced rear subframe and preventative rod bearing replacement already performed. Every suspension bushing remains tight, and the factory dampers retain original damping rates for surgical turn-in. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
